# Proposal Types

This project has multiple governance proposal types with distinct vote structures, status logic, and data shapes.

**Before writing or modifying any proposal component or vote calculation, read the relevant docs:**

- Index + shared concepts (vote weights, status flow, voter groups): [`docs/PROPOSAL_TYPES.md`](../../docs/PROPOSAL_TYPES.md)
- Individual types: [`docs/proposal-types/`](../../docs/proposal-types/)

## Quick type lookup

| Type | Source | Key signal |
|---|---|---|
| STANDARD | `dao_node` | `hybrid=false`, `voting_module_name="standard"` |
| HYBRID_STANDARD | `dao_node`+`eas-atlas` | `hybrid=true`, `voting_module_name="standard"` |
| APPROVAL | `dao_node` | `hybrid=false`, `voting_module_name="approval"` |
| HYBRID_APPROVAL | `dao_node`+`eas-atlas` | `hybrid=true`, `voting_module_name="approval"` |
| OPTIMISTIC | `dao_node` | `hybrid=false`, `voting_module_name="optimistic"` |
| HYBRID_OPTIMISTIC_TIERED | `dao_node`+`eas-atlas` | `hybrid=true`, `tiers` has values |
| OFFCHAIN_OPTIMISTIC | `eas-atlas` | `proposal_type="OPTIMISTIC"`, `tiers=[]` |
| OFFCHAIN_OPTIMISTIC_TIERED | `eas-atlas` | `proposal_type="OPTIMISTIC_TIERED"` |
| OFFCHAIN_STANDARD | `eas-oodao` | source=`eas-oodao` |

## Critical shared concepts

- **Hybrid vote weights**: delegates=50%, users=~16.67%, apps=~16.67%, chains=~16.67%
- **Eligible counts**: USER=1000, APP=100, CHAIN=15
- **Status order**: terminal states (cancel/execute/queue) → timing (PENDING/ACTIVE) → vote-based
- **HYBRID_STANDARD status**: OR logic — passes if threshold OR quorum met (not AND)
- **Optimistic proposals**: SUCCEEDED by default unless veto threshold triggered
